701234f-a.title: Bronx: Havemeyer Avenue - Waterbury Avenue
701234f-a.text:
1306 Havemeyer Avenue, east side, between Waterbury and
Vestchester Avenues . On the left is visible the elevated trestle of
the I.R.T. subway.
April 16, 1938
P. L. Sperr
